葛培理患有脑积水、柏金逊病和前列腺癌。因為健康的關係，2008年後早已淡出傳道，由兒子[[葛福臨|葛福臨]]接替其工作。葛培理於2018年2月21日於美国北卡罗莱那州蒙特里特家中逝世，[[訃告|享耆壽]]99歲。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/21/obituaries/billy-graham-dead.html|title=Billy Graham, 99, Dies; Pastor Filled Stadiums and Counseled Presidents|last=Goodstein|first=Laurie|date=2018-02-21|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-02-21|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419073210/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/21/obituaries/billy-graham-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

